42:56.033 --> 43:01.802
I pray, O God, that we would continually fall more in love with Jesus.

43:03.224 --> 43:07.429
I'm being amazed who He is and worshiping Him for His glorious grace.

43:08.411 --> 43:11.195
Gee, thank you Lord for this wonderful truth.

43:11.996 --> 43:13.458
We rest in you, O God.

43:13.602 --> 43:14.926
in Jesus' name we pray.

43:14.946 --> 43:17.615
You know, all God's people said, Amen.

43:18.318 --> 43:23.314
If you're here today and don't know Jesus, please don't leave our campus without trusting in Christ.

43:23.650 --> 43:24.811
at the close of our service.

43:24.851 --> 43:28.374
We're going to have some encouragers here at the front who would love to talk with you.

43:28.654 --> 43:30.696
They'll be here at the steps here to answer questions.

43:30.716 --> 43:32.758
You'll be like, I don't know how to put my faith in Jesus.

43:33.178 --> 43:33.939
Come and talk with them.

43:33.959 --> 43:35.360
They would love to talk with you.

43:35.841 --> 43:41.646
If you have something going on in your life, which you want someone to pray with you, they would be honored to pray with you today.

43:41.666 --> 43:45.049
I want to say thank you for your generosity and your giving.

43:45.649 --> 43:48.151
There are buckets out in the atrium in which you can give.

43:48.432 --> 43:50.894
You can also give online through the Westwood app.

43:50.914 --> 43:53.636
Because of your giving, this gospel is going forth all

43:53.616 --> 43:55.079
over the world.

43:55.419 --> 43:56.882
Teenagers are getting baptized.

43:57.102 --> 43:58.444
We're sending mission teams.

43:58.805 --> 44:00.268
I mean, God is doing incredible work.

44:00.428 --> 44:04.916
We are doing a pre-teen conference for fourth through sixth graders coming up in two weeks.

44:05.276 --> 44:06.158
You won't want to miss it.

44:06.719 --> 44:09.804
Now, I introduced last week this idea of the ping pong balls.

44:09.824 --> 44:12.629
If you weren't here, I introduced this to our faith family.

44:13.451 --> 44:17.778
What we're doing as a faith family in 2026 is we're encouraging you to share the gospel.

44:18.178 --> 44:23.966
So if you have a teammate, a co-worker, a neighbor, a child, a grandchild, we want you sharing the gospel.

44:24.567 --> 44:34.721
So every time you share the gospel, when you come to church, we want you to write that person's first name or their initials, and you can drop it in the box out in the atrium.

44:34.781 --> 44:43.152
It says, we are sent, and it's got this plexiglass cover, and we're gonna fill that thing up because each ball represents a gospel conversation.

44:43.713 --> 44:47.378
Doesn't mean that you're leading someone to faith in Jesus, although you might get to do that.

44:47.682 --> 44:51.569
But if you're just taking these gospel moments and you're sharing Jesus, we wanna celebrate that.

44:52.009 --> 44:57.298
We wanna see a tangible growth of the number of gospel conversations we as a faith family are having.

44:57.599 --> 45:02.387
Now we also have one of these boxes with these ping pong balls upstairs for the student ministry.

45:02.968 --> 45:07.756
Currently, adults, they have more balls of gospel conversations than you do.

45:09.639 --> 45:13.586
So, as someone who is uber competitive,

45:15.298 --> 45:16.881
I think we should step up our game.

45:17.081 --> 45:17.502
What do you say?

45:17.522 --> 45:18.745
All right.

45:19.386 --> 45:20.628
Let's start sharing the gospel.

45:21.169 --> 45:22.411
And we'll just keep celebrating that.

45:23.253 --> 45:25.958
Church, I want you to know, I'm just absolutely crazy about you.

45:26.860 --> 45:28.403
I love you so much.

45:28.423 --> 45:30.286
But Jesus lets you learn.

45:30.306 --> 45:33.192
Let's call him in the back of Jesus.

45:33.212 --> 45:34.354
God, let's praise the Lord.

